58441,"uid":34144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e5a5765fd4b3d5b790acdc93062095bbab3ed79e","tid":1658441,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"036b3aededc1db0e58385805e656596a99776d68","tid":1658441,"uid":296825,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1f771f1ad5a835503b65ee74bc8cec05016daf2c","tid":1658441,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hiLa33w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhiLa33w.png&h=881f1343&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點睇都係想打壓嚇鳩你遊行啦下嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想選到咁使唔使咁猴擒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:36:33.000Z","msg":"一開始覺得一定係關星期日遊行事，但一位心水清嘅朋友點醒咗我 以下係佢嘅理論：<br />\n<br />\n保皇黨知道今次區選一定輸，唯有趁住區選提名就嚟截止，攻擊一個曝光率高嘅對家候選人 - 例如岑子杰呢啲曾經受襲嘅人!<br />\n<br />\n目標唔只係岑子杰，其實係想令大量參選素人因為危險而唔敢參選，或者畀屋企人逼佢哋退選!<br />\n<br />\n喺提名截止之後可能會再有人遇襲，因為截止之後有人退選，就冇得再揾人頂上，所以更加有利保皇黨!<br />\n<br />\n未必因為遊行原因： 因為如果岑子杰受傷，反而會多咗人出泥遊行咁簡單嘅事冇理由估唔到。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭同黑警一定要周9，但係亦都唔好唔記得李慧瓊同何君堯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:38:24.000Z","msg":"得啦得啦，選贏會有五大訴求？白痴都知唔會。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:49:29.000Z","msg":"你講下做乜撚嘢先會達成五大訴犬水嚟聽下？前議助邱生？<br />\n<br />\n呢樣又話冇用，嗰樣又屌鳩人血饅頭，屌你老母唔係兄弟爬山，各自努力咩？私怨柒頭縮撚返入個閪度啦屌你老母。"},{"pid":"629847c6a672c2bfbf9e6a3ea3ec28abf69de50b","tid":1658441,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-